Now I need to count how many medals Geoff Hunt won in his twenties. Since he was born in 1947:
- His twenties: Age 20-29 means years 1967 to 1976 (inclusive)
  
Looking at the medals, only the 1976 medal falls within his twenties. Let me write the SQL query to count this:

function.arguments:
{"command": "cat <<'EOF' > /tmp/query.sql
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM medal m
JOIN format f ON m.format_id = f.format_id
JOIN tournament t ON f.tournament_id = t.tournament_id
JOIN personalinformation p ON t.athlete_id = p.athlete_id
WHERE t.athlete_id = 1
  AND m.year >= p.birth_year + 20
  AND m.year <= p.birth_year + 29;
EOF
cat /tmp/query.sql
"}
